---
import Layout from '../../../../site-layouts/Layout.astro';
import GeekSpellBaseStyles from '../../../../components/geekspell/GeekSpellBaseStyles.astro';

const YT_ID = 'z7IKhvnVems';
const YT_EMBED = `https://www.youtube.com/embed/${YT_ID}`;
const YT_WATCH = `https://youtu.be/${YT_ID}`;
---

<Layout title="EP07 · Agent vs Skill vs Workflow | GeekSpell" lang="en">
  <GeekSpellBaseStyles />
  <main class="gs-ep-page">
    <div class="gs-wrap">
      <p class="gs-crumb">
        <a href="/en/">Archive</a> · <a href="/en/geekspell/">GeekSpell</a> · EP07
      </p>
      <p class="gs-eyebrow">GeekSpell literacy EP07 · English · Skill &amp; Workflow</p>
      <h1>Agent vs Skill vs Workflow</h1>
      <p class="gs-lead">
        Calling an agent is not enough. Separate worker, tool, and pipeline — that is how agents
        become efficient and controllable.
      </p>
      <div class="gs-player">
        <iframe
          src={YT_EMBED}
          title="GeekSpell EP07 EN"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <p class="gs-links">
        <a href="/en/geekspell/ep06-agent-team/">← EP06 Agent team</a>
        ·
        <a href="/zh/geekspell/ep07-skill-workflow/">中文 EP07</a>
        ·
        <a href="/ja/geekspell/ep07-skill-workflow/">日本語 EP07</a>
        ·
        <a href={YT_WATCH} target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>
      </p>
      <section class="gs-body">
        <h2>What you will learn (step by step)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Agent</strong> = worker under goals and permissions
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Skill</strong> = reusable tool with clear input → output
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Workflow</strong> = ordered pipeline of skills with handoffs
          </li>
          <li>Define skills first, then workflow, then assign agents</li>
          <li>Copy the five-field template before you open a long chat</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Series path</h2>
        <p>
          EP05 acceptance → EP06 team → <strong>EP07 tools &amp; pipelines</strong> → EP08 one-page
          closed loop.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
